  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7770b5cae0c15f601f86a0bf0cfc9489.poster.avif?t=1759573750\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7770b5cae0c15f601f86a0bf0cfc9489.webm?t=1759573750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7770b5cae0c15f601f86a0bf0cfc9489.mp4?t=1759573750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling adventure in Pre Dusk, a captivating journey into darkness. Play as Ray, a determined youth escaping his grandfather's mysterious home. Master weapons and abilities like gliding and grappling to overcome challenges and foes. Uncover secrets, interact with intriguing characters, and navigate diverse environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Predusk is rich with its characters and natural diversity where each level brings new visual experiences and gameplay challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use multiple weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock new abilities at every level  [Gliding,  double jump, Grappling, Crossbow]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore the natural diversity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Classic side-scrolling action, with all the modern art style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fight your way through dozens of creatures who want to stop you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- explore secret rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The controls are simple and accessible - simply jump, Attack, Swim, and double jump, Where you can use your controller for the best experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Talk to different characters and face difficult challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/b5c914522b18122e94459916f26ff5bf.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each aspect of the game art and characters is hand-drawn with passion and regard to the world and lore of the game.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/13370f4510f38dde7d9d873c16934b72.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/10ce594d0b1cdf59b846e5332c2274dc.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>Explore a haunting black and white 2D world filled with dark caves and face off against a fearsome crow boss in this intense platforming adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/a205bb254b2abd66c380a6f70696d1ab.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>Brave the icy depths of Brain Freeze, a cold blue level filled with stunning landscapes, treacherous ice caves, and challenging enemies in this action-packed adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/948eed15c03d0f5c46b85fae828540de.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>Step into the misty and mysterious Foggy Forest where you'll encounter weird characters, battle a formidable tree boss, and conquer diverse platforming challenges in this green forest game level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/021e3138a9ed53f192a50864e9e43e39.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=192 /></span><br>Jump into the dangers of the Savage Sands, a sand desert level filled with ancient castles, tough platforming, and fearsome sandworm enemies, in this exciting adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/e1032d980d3021ea5601383fd1ac8dc6.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>In the final showdown at Castle Rain, you'll face the game's most powerful character and his formidable castle guard enemies while navigating challenging platforming in this intense last level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7ba6528971b9cca0910e9039bb5cdfd7.avif?t=1759573750\" width=603 height=283 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7770b5cae0c15f601f86a0bf0cfc9489.poster.avif?t=1759573750\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7770b5cae0c15f601f86a0bf0cfc9489.webm?t=1759573750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7770b5cae0c15f601f86a0bf0cfc9489.mp4?t=1759573750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling adventure in Pre Dusk, a captivating journey into darkness. Play as Ray, a determined youth escaping his grandfather's mysterious home. Master weapons and abilities like gliding and grappling to overcome challenges and foes. Uncover secrets, interact with intriguing characters, and navigate diverse environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Predusk is rich with its characters and natural diversity where each level brings new visual experiences and gameplay challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use multiple weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock new abilities at every level  [Gliding,  double jump, Grappling, Crossbow]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore the natural diversity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Classic side-scrolling action, with all the modern art style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fight your way through dozens of creatures who want to stop you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- explore secret rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The controls are simple and accessible - simply jump, Attack, Swim, and double jump, Where you can use your controller for the best experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Talk to different characters and face difficult challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/b5c914522b18122e94459916f26ff5bf.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each aspect of the game art and characters is hand-drawn with passion and regard to the world and lore of the game.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/13370f4510f38dde7d9d873c16934b72.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/10ce594d0b1cdf59b846e5332c2274dc.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>Explore a haunting black and white 2D world filled with dark caves and face off against a fearsome crow boss in this intense platforming adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/a205bb254b2abd66c380a6f70696d1ab.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>Brave the icy depths of Brain Freeze, a cold blue level filled with stunning landscapes, treacherous ice caves, and challenging enemies in this action-packed adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/948eed15c03d0f5c46b85fae828540de.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>Step into the misty and mysterious Foggy Forest where you'll encounter weird characters, battle a formidable tree boss, and conquer diverse platforming challenges in this green forest game level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/021e3138a9ed53f192a50864e9e43e39.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=192 /></span><br>Jump into the dangers of the Savage Sands, a sand desert level filled with ancient castles, tough platforming, and fearsome sandworm enemies, in this exciting adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/e1032d980d3021ea5601383fd1ac8dc6.avif?t=1759573750\" width=604 height=174 /></span><br>In the final showdown at Castle Rain, you'll face the game's most powerful character and his formidable castle guard enemies while navigating challenging platforming in this intense last level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721680/extras/7ba6528971b9cca0910e9039bb5cdfd7.avif?t=1759573750\" width=603 height=283 /></span></p>",
